{"id":25,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22910,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":25,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},[".title","The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f1"},[".credit",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"Matt and Mandy’s family is moving to a different city because of Dad’s job."]],["div",{"id":"f2","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f2"},["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"I’m leaving all of my friends behind!"]],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f3"},["div",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"Don’t worry, Matt. You make friends a lot easier than I do."],["div",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"Yeah, I guess. But I still don’t know where my new school is. Or where my class will be. I’m sure I’ll get lost."]],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f4"},["div",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"It’s scary right now because the future is foggy—like that day last winter when we got lost driving home from the movies."],["div",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"That was actually kind of a fun adventure …"]],["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f5"},["div",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"But we have each other, and we have the gospel. And if we hold on tight to those things, everything will work out."]],["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f6"},["div",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"Hmm. Fog? Holding on tight? Hey! It’s like Lehi’s dream in the Book of Mormon—holding on to the iron rod."],["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p11"},"I guess it is."]],["div",{"id":"f7","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f7"},["div",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p12"},"And guess what else. Mandy, you know you’ve been looking forward to being old enough to go to the temple to do baptisms for the dead?"],["div",{"id":"p13","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p13"},"Mandy: Yes?"]],["div",{"id":"f8","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f8"},["div",{"id":"p14","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p14"},"Well, our new home will be much closer to a temple."],["div",{"id":"p15","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p15"},"Cool!"]],["div",{"id":"p16","uri":"/friend/2013/03/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p16"},"(To be continued.)"]]],"refs":null}
